{"tid":1021448,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片慎入] 山東大媽公園吊住頸跳廣場舞，稱可治頸椎","createTime":"2019-02-14T09:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T07:28:49.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"53bbdd51689c204260ce8110ecceab9bf51a41f4","tid":1021448,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:06:52.000Z","msg":"【山東大媽公園「吊頸」跳廣場舞】<br />\n【嚇到街坊生人勿近　實情為治頸椎】<br />\n<br />\n事先聲明，片段並非死亡直播，但家庭觀眾亦切勿模仿。<br />\n<br />\n正所謂，古有小龍女以繩為床，今有山東大媽「吊頸」跳廣場舞。自信的表情，舉手投足間充滿閒暇，這個大媽每日都要在公園吊足半個鐘，過去一年日日如是，臉不紅耳不赤：「半個小時，音響不響了我就下來了。怎麼撐，撐一天都沒事，睡覺睏了，在上頭睡一會也行。」<br />\n<br />\n不過略嫌裝束遠看好像紙紮公仔，嚇到街坊生人勿近！這「堅離地操」能否減雙下巴不得而知，宋連雲指對自己就有神奇功效，不但醫好頸椎病，六十八歲的她平時連藥物都不用服吃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2034855243325618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2034855243325618&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDlA4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=00a68fdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2034855243325618</a>"},{"pid":"e7b4e7d12df496bb30a74f62b5526e5f0b4e9ba2","tid":1021448,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"617b1aa3c5cf1eeed7bfa7f5e093bbf3ff675e3a","tid":1021448,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"無科學根據都夠擔做"},{"pid":"46a02a924b852d06814acff50f24f5e753ec8747","tid":1021448,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"咁仲有頸椎科醫生托7咩"},{"pid":"c5853c5acb84d3d0b749f60f08e281a39511c95e","tid":1021448,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"617b1aa3c5cf1eeed7bfa7f5e093bbf3ff675e3a","tid":1021448,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"無科學根據都夠擔做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:11:53.000Z","msg":"其實有，但係正常做法係坐嚮度，同埋用滑輪自己調鬆緊"},{"pid":"cb371cd8c981068d9caa26e199c7f54399016bce","tid":1021448,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfa35ee08ca1e71804c9da8265acc6454d8dd04","tid":1021448,"uid":32260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:13:09.000Z","msg":"大媽既做法，係理論上正確<br />\n不過就難睇啲咁囉"},{"pid":"861f3506b6edebf4e9391f1983607ca93530588c","tid":1021448,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:15:23.000Z","msg":"山東大媽「吊頸操」治療頸椎病 脊醫：搵命搏隨時喪失活動能力<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2271411/大媽「吊頸操」治療頸椎病%20脊醫：搵命搏隨時喪失活動能力\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2271411%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E3%80%8C%E5%90%8A%E9%A0%B8%E6%93%8D%E3%80%8D%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82%E9%A0%B8%E6%A4%8E%E7%97%85%2520%E8%84%8A%E9%86%AB%EF%BC%9A%E6%90%B5%E5%91%BD%E6%90%8F%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E5%96%AA%E5%A4%B1%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDlA4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=cb818c25\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2271411/大媽「吊頸操」治療頸椎病%20脊醫：搵命搏隨時喪失活動能力</a><br />\n<br />\n頸椎病困擾不少人，最近山東青島有一位68歲的大媽，過去一年每日都在公園利用特製的工具進行「吊頸式」健身訓練30分鐘，並聲稱治療了頸椎病。有脊骨神經科醫生表示，這種模仿物理治療頸椎牽引的動作，如沒有經專業診斷而進行，如同搵命搏，隨時影響手腳活動能力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2270000/2271411/mama01_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2270000%2F2271411%2Fmama01_600.jpg&h=27df5507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這位山東大媽每日都會利用她特製的工具來進行吊頸操，在音樂配合下在空中雙腳堅離地跳舞。據了解，她早年因為勞損而得頸椎病，連低頭也不可以，但自從每天做這個吊頸式運動半小時，持續一年，聲稱治好了頸椎病，而且可以持續一天都沒事，甚至以吊着頸來睡一會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2270000/2271411/mama02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2270000%2F2271411%2Fmama02_600.jpg&h=504187f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n脊骨神經科醫生王俊華表示，這種做法跟物理治療所用的頸椎牽引類似，但要知道物理治療師或脊醫為有頸椎受壓問題的患者進行頸椎牽引時，是要配合肌肉放鬆及消炎，並要在一個穩定的地方坐好及要調整好適當的力度及方法去做，而絕不是這位婆婆的做法，「她吊着條頸擢住，有機會拉傷，因為頸椎十分脆弱，而她讓力量集中下半身墜，甚至有機會造成骨折或韌帶撕裂問題，加上她年事已高，如果本身有骨質疏鬆問題，風險則更大。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2270000/2271411/drwongchuwa14022019_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2270000%2F2271411%2Fdrwongchuwa14022019_600.jpg&h=b3c17f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王俊華又補充，如果經過正式診斷而配合頸椎牽引儀器，的確是一個治療程序，但如果未經醫生診斷而做，則是「搵命博」，「如果剛巧能拉鬆她頸椎壓位置，又剛好沒有整傷她的話，也可能會有治療效果，但如果擢的力度太大或擢得太突如其來，反而有可能弄傷脊髓，影響手腳活動，甚至完全失去活動能力，實在不宜為了一個未必有真正治療效果的動作而冒險。」"},{"pid":"2ee7ddea34e85b0d3d16654d52a296ba674935f1","tid":1021448,"uid":75765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:19:16.000Z","msg":"準備練30年, 到時大派用場"},{"pid":"67c57825d966a8a2802ae6560b3ca20043b87a3a","tid":1021448,"uid":182864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:43:32.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 如果拉後頸條帶再落多幾cm<br />\n頸後動脈俾唔到血落腦<br />\n十幾秒之內會失去知覺<br />\n十幾分鐘就會腦死亡<br />\n俾著我都唔夠膽啦"},{"pid":"4cf583f69c881d629e9276a235fa0d9ed47ae441","tid":1021448,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ee7ddea34e85b0d3d16654d52a296ba674935f1","tid":1021448,"uid":75765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:19:16.000Z","msg":"準備練30年, 到時大派用場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:49:47.000Z","msg":"但前面果場喊戲NG左十幾次阻住曬？"},{"pid":"ed047ec6adfcd899e9305115856e1b1f12ffd958","tid":1021448,"uid":112355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:17:02.000Z","msg":"Natural selection<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2144c6028a3f6e36755ef69e31d936c5be18212","tid":1021448,"uid":236401,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68840719513d684b5d4852f0952e3eed225f4fc7","tid":1021448,"uid":54516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"正宗吊老母"},{"pid":"70204b55e002a606496febc436268fe1c2468814","tid":1021448,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"只有死先可以醫到愚蠢"},{"pid":"6b6ea4c4092cd1a607e6ba149b72a76cc8bc42b5","tid":1021448,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"></span>"},{"pid":"3bde5ec1434cb7b48d95f348d8d304bf5872e659","tid":1021448,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70204b55e002a606496febc436268fe1c2468814","tid":1021448,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"只有死先可以醫到愚蠢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:34:41.000Z","msg":"其實唔on9"},{"pid":"e5287850fe0e83b5042634ed0c380990f51cb8b4","tid":1021448,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T06:14:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"></span>"},{"pid":"fd119e4935c4f0ed71f831b46995ce64131fb409","tid":1021448,"uid":87573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"有時頸痛真係好難頂，用類似原理舒緩係幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然個大媽做得真係幾嚇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}